{"name":"Sorcelet: Flétrissement Mineur","permission":{"default":0,"5bOYsTte0hqZOsUh":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>De l&rsquo;&eacute;nergie n&eacute;crotique s&rsquo;insinue dans un objet ou une cr&eacute;ature&nbsp;de votre choix. Si vous ciblez un objet organique, il&nbsp;pourrit. Un min&eacute;ral devient friable. Le m&eacute;tal rouille et devient&nbsp;cassant. En termes de r&egrave;gles, la CA de ces objets diminue de&nbsp;2 points. Si vous ciblez une cr&eacute;ature, celle-ci subit 1d4 points&nbsp;de d&eacute;g&acirc;ts n&eacute;crotiques si elle rate un jet de sauvegarde de&nbsp;Constitution. Ce sort n&rsquo;a pas d&rsquo;effet sur un mort-vivant ou&nbsp;une cr&eacute;ature artificielle. Aux niveaux sup&eacute;rieurs, la CA des&nbsp;objets diminue de 1 point suppl&eacute;mentaire au niveau 5 (-3), au&nbsp;niveau 11 (-4) et au niveau 17 (-5).</p>\n<p><em>Note : ce sorcelet est fort utile pour les artisans travaillant sur&nbsp;le bois, la pierre ou le m&eacute;tal, ainsi que pour les sapeurs&hellip;</em></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":9,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[["1d4","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"level":0,"school":"nec","components":{"value":"","vocal":true,"somatic":true,"material":false,"ritual":false,"concentration":false},"materials":{"value":"","consumed":false,"cost":0,"supply":0},"preparation":{"mode":"prepared","prepared":false},"scaling":{"mode":"cantrip","formula":"+1"}},"flags":{"dynamiceffects":{"equipActive":[true,true],"alwaysActive":[true,true]},"mess":{"templateTexture":"","isBonusDamag